                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 16, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am preparing correspondence relating to the <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi>
                    case which is voluminous and important, mostly in Spanish, which I am
                    translating. Can not be transmitted before next week.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
